description:
This is a 10 minute workout called 'Treadmill Running Form For Beginners' from the channel The Run Experience.
The workout falls under Cardio/Treadmill and Cardio/Running.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Foundation Builder vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: In this video we give you the "rundown" on treadmill running form for beginners! Learn how to run indoors, how to safely get off the treadmill without interrupting your workout, and what to look for in your posture and cadence as you go.
